codingRNA\_fam: A string indicating the name of the miRNA family the~miRNA belongs to. feature: A string indicating the feature annotation on the genome where the~binding site occurs. label: A boolean value indicating whether the example belongs to the positive or negative class. chr: A string indicating the chromosome number on the genome where the binding site occurs. start: An integer indicating the 1-based start position of the binding site on the genome. end: An integer indicating the 1-based end position of the binding site on the~genome. strand: A string indicating whether the binding site occurs on the ’+’ or ’-’ strand~on the genome. gene\_cluster\_ID: An integer indicating the cluster ID of the binding site sequence used to generate the negative class.},
